info.description:
Run the Tests
-------------

Install tox and run it::

    pip install tox
    tox

Limit the tests to a specific python version::

    tox -e py27

Conventions
-----------

Onegov Org follows PEP8 as close as possible. To test for it run::

    tox -e pep8

Onegov Org uses `Semantic Versioning <http://semver.org/>`_

info.html_description:
Run the Tests

Install tox and run it:

pip install tox
tox

Limit the tests to a specific python version:

tox -e py27

Conventions

Onegov Org follows PEP8 as close as possible. To test for it run:

tox -e pep8

Onegov Org uses Semantic Versioning
